bikin file crt, key, dan csr
https://en.rakko.tools/tools/46/

converter
https://www.sslshopper.com/ssl-converter.html

instal openssl
- https://slproweb.com/products/Win32OpenSSL.html
- masukin folder bin C:\Program Files\OpenSSL-Win64\bin --> ke cari di windows search "env" atau "system environment variable"
- paste directory bin openssl ke bagian "Path" tabg "system"
referensi https://www.ryadel.com/en/openssl-convert-ssl-certificates-pem-crt-cer-pfx-p12-linux-windows/#Installing_OpenSSL

sytax openssl
- bikin pfx/p12 --> openssl pkcs12 -export -in code.crt -inkey code.key -out code.p12
  - atau bisa menggunakan software "wondershare pdf element pro 7.4 / 8.0"
- lihat isi file --> openssl x509 -text -noout -in code.p12
